title: Depression - Episode 2

embed.description: What shall occur in this week's episode of the Depressed Ranked Team? Sit back, Relax & Enjoy! Music by Kevin MacLeod http://incompetech.com/ Music by Tobu http://www.youtube.com/tobuofficial

body:
Hey Guys, XSirCution here and we are thinking of creating a YouTube series for our ranked team.
So let me know if you guys enjoyed the video and subscribe to see more! 

Remember.. Always play a real champion like {{champion:11}} 

-XSirCution

replies.body: That was fun! You guys look like you're having a great time - and that made me feel like i was having a great time. Keep it up :)

I wouldn't say getting ulted by Nocturne all the time was great but Thank you for the comment!
We really appreciate it :)
